metadata.name: Through the chaos
metadata.description:
"Words are not needed here.

All I require is a single touch, and all of you will gush to me like the great ocean waves.

Your past, your present, your dreams, your secrets, your worries, I can see it vividly before me.

I see what you require of me, and I can, indeed, help you fulfill it.

Now, are you prepared to make our contract binding?"
